title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sightseeing - Flying over Spa
description:
In this video we will fly over the the F1 Circuit Spa Francorchamps while we are on our way to Bahrain for some F1 winter testing.

After we passed Spa shortly you will hear the Bushtalk radio client kicking in and providing some nice explanation about the circuit.

If you also want to have some nice explanations about POI's which you are passing during your flight go the to site of Bushtalk radio and download their client:

https://bushtalkradio.com/
